Package model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IFixedPortfolio
    This Interface that describes all the operations that can be performed on a fixed portfolio.
    IFlexiblePortfolio
    The interface for Flexible portfolio.
    IstockModel
    Interface IstockModel describes how a stock would look like.
    IUserInterface
    Interface to describe methods for a User of the stock market application.
